data.description: MLS# 272032 Don't miss out on the spacious four bedroom, three bathroom home located in West Pasco just blocks from Liberty Park! As you walk up to this home you will be greeted by an oversized covered porch. Upon entering you will be welcomed with a large living room with an adorable bay window. You will pass through a dining room that's big enough for all the family gatherings. From there you will enter into the updated kitchen with quartz countertops, full tile back splash, new dishwasher and an easy to clean glass top stove. The kitchen is open to a welcoming family room with vinyl plank flooring and charming paneling. All 4 bedrooms are located upstairs. The beautiful master bedroom has custom built ins with a custom bench. The master bathroom has a separate jetted tub, double vanity with quartz countertop and a huge walk in closet. The large remaining 3 bedrooms have plenty of room for everyone and 2 have walk in closets. There is a cute updated full bathroom upstairs and good sized laundry room. All carpet upstairs is brand new, the living room carpet was replaced a year ago. The fully fenced back yard has an oversized patio with a portion of it covered, and a great fire pit perfect for outside gatherings. Don't forget this home also has a three car garage so plenty of room for all your toys. Call your favorite realtor today and schedule a showing!
